About us

Quantum Gravity - is a WEB 3.0 era game and software development studio started in 2021 by a team experienced in Gaming and Blockchain.

Our mission is to go beyond the traditional approach to game development to bring more rights to the players and scale games to the modern economy models without intermediaries.

We want to create leading industry products that are made by players for players. We want to create leading industry products that are made by players for players.

Services

Game development

We provide full-cycle game development from scratch, whether an indie project or AAA game.

Our team will save you time and money and create a project combining fascinating mechanics, high-quality graphics, and the implementation of cutting-edge technology.

We design plots and stories combined with unique game art solutions. Unique ideas, sappy animations, and vivid characters define our projects and strengthen clients' dreams!

Blockchain integration

We can implement a blockchain and Play-To-Earn economy into any game and bridge the gap between Web2 and Web3 gaming by providing an easy and fast solution.

Create value for players inside a game economy, making them the real owners of their assets. We enable incentivizing playing through asset ownership using NFT technology.

Let your players own their digital assets and create content, trade them with no trouble, and have fun in the meantime! Monetize your game through the implementation of blockchain and cryptocurrencies.

Publishment

We can bring to real life any of your ideas using the most efficient and fast methodology to lift your game on top.

We want to drive the industry by boosting the most talented developers. We are ready not only to test the product but also to support your team financially.

Our team takes care of every slightest thing. We test, create an iteration roadmap and promote and monetize your game to bring it on top.

What we are building

Elementies

Elementies is a Pokemon-inspired, play-to-earn game universe that uses the Solana blockchain. The games main characters are Elementies, NFT tokens used in-game.

Elementies will allow players to earn rewards by winning battles, collaborating with other players, breeding, raising, collecting, selling, renting property, and much more.

Orion Shelter

Orion Shelter is the first community-owned decentralized virtual space project, where all decisions are made by the DAO members formed into two main factions. Thirteen races, with their characteristics and abilities, correspond to twenty ideal professions on the ship.

Coming soon

Womeverse

Womeverse is a women-led initiative that seeks to unite women through both present and future opportunities. Our values are embodied through education, a craving for beauty&sustainability, and mutual help.

Quantum Gravity helped prepare the ERC-721a contract for the minting event and NFTs generation.

We continue to build on our incredible portfolio - from first-to-market innovations to beautiful versions of the games people know and love.
